subject: French Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Venus Williams, struggling with a sore back and nearing the end of her career, fell to 37th-ranked Urszula Radwanska, 7-6 (5), 6-7 (4), 6-4, in the first round of the French Open.
